---
const INSTAGRAM_URL = "https://www.instagram.com/lawyer.nakanohito/";
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>ページが見つかりません｜中の人ナビ</title>
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;700;900&family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/detective/styles.css?v=20260615b" />
  <style>
    .nf-wrap {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: var(--beige);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .nf-body {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 3rem 1.25rem;
    }
    .nf-card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 480px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    }
    .nf-emoji { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .nf-card h1 {
      font-family: var(--serif);
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      color: var(--navy);
      margin-bottom: .75rem;
    }
    .nf-card p { font-size: .92rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .nf-links {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: .65rem;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .nf-link {
      background: var(--beige);
      border: 1px solid var(--beige-mid);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: .85rem 1rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .75rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--text);
      transition: all .18s;
    }
    .nf-link:hover { border-color: var(--gold); background: #fff; text-decoration: none; }
    .nf-link-icon { font-size: 1.4rem; }
    .nf-link strong { display: block; font-size: .9rem; color: var(--navy); }
    .nf-link span { display: block; font-size: .75rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: .15rem; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="dt-header">
  <div class="dt-header-inner">
    <a href="/detective/" class="dt-logo">
      <div class="dt-logo-icon"><img src="/detective/images/logo-icon.png" alt="弁護士の中の人" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;border-radius:8px;display:block;" /></div>
      <div class="dt-logo-wrap"><span>弁護士の中の人</span><span class="dt-logo-sub">中の人ナビ</span></div>
    </a>
    <a href={INSTAGRAM_URL} class="dt-header-insta" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" ry="5"/><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"/></svg>
      <span>@lawyer.nakanohito</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="nf-wrap">
  <div class="nf-body">
    <div class="nf-card">
      <div class="nf-emoji">🔍</div>
      <h1>ページが見つかりませんでした</h1>
      <p>お探しのページは、移動または削除された可能性があります。<br/>下のリンクから目的の情報を探してみてください。</p>
      <div class="nf-links">
        <a href="/detective/" class="nf-link">
          <span class="nf-link-icon">🏠</span>
          <div><strong>TOPページ</strong><span>サイト全体のはじまり</span></div>
        </a>
        <a href="/detective/start/" class="nf-link">
          <span class="nf-link-icon">📘</span>
          <div><strong>最初にやること</strong><span>浮気を疑ったら、まず読むガイド</span></div>
        </a>
        <a href="/detective/flow/" class="nf-link">
          <span class="nf-link-icon">🧭</span>
          <div><strong>どれから始める？</strong><span>状況別の選択肢ガイド</span></div>
        </a>
        <a href="/detective/column/" class="nf-link">
          <span class="nf-link-icon">📖</span>
          <div><strong>コラムを読む</strong><span>事務員目線の体験談・選択肢の整理</span></div>
        </a>
        <a href="/detective/about/" class="nf-link">
          <span class="nf-link-icon">👤</span>
          <div><strong>中の人について</strong><span>運営者プロフィール</span></div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
